description:
Expand your track list with the Chart Hits Song Pack! You need the full game Let's Sing Country to use this DLC. Includes hit songs:
• Clean Bandit “Tears”
• Lost Frequencies feat. Janieck Devy “Reality”
• Sigala “Sweet Lovin”
• Galantis “No Money”
• Jonas Blue/ JP Cooper “Perfect Strangers”
name: Let's Sing - Chart Hits Song Pack
